Package org.jpws.pwslib.order

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Collatable
    Defining a class which bears a CollationKey.
    OrderedListListener
    Interface for a listener to an ordered record list as represented by the class OrderedRecordList.
    OrderedRecordList.RecordSelector
    Interface to define filtering criteria for this ordered list via the accept() method.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayIterator<T>  
    DefaultRecordWrapper
    This class wraps a PwsRecord for purposes of quick reference to a listing sort value derived from and belonging to the record.
    OrderedListEvent
    Event issued for an OrderedListListener.
    OrderedRecordList
    Represents an ordered list of DefaultRecordWrapper objects which may (or may not) belong to a specific, singular PwsRecordList.
